```graphql
query GetproductList($take: Int = 10, $skip: Int = 0, $ids: [Int] ,$product_specification_middle_price_id: [Int] , $product_categories: Int, $name: String, $is_deleted: Int, $is_custom_rule: Int, $dividend_type: Int, $store_id: Int, $tag_id: [Int], $orderBy: [localhost_productOrderByWithRelationInput], $product_type: Boolean, $stock_status: Int, $status: Int) {
  data: localhost_findManyproduct(
    skip: $skip
    take: $take
    where: {id:{in: $ids},product_specification_middle_price :{every:{id:{in: $product_specification_middle_price_id}}}product_categories: {is: {id: {equals: $product_categories}}}, name: {contains: $name}, is_deleted: {equals: $is_deleted}, product_dividend: {every: {is_deleted: {equals: 0}, is_custom_rule: {equals: $is_custom_rule}, dividend_type: {equals: $dividend_type}}}, store_id: {equals: $store_id}, product_tag_mapping: {every: {tag_id: {in: $tag_id}, dr: {equals: 0}}}, product_type: {equals: $product_type}, stock_status: {equals: $stock_status}, status: {equals: $status}}
    orderBy: $orderBy
  ) {
    id
    store_id
    name
    type
    subtitle
    price
    market_price
    cost_price
    stock
    stock_status
    status
    link_pc
    link_applet
    link_computer
    created_at
    updated_at
    deleted_at
    is_deleted
    category_id
    product_discount{
       id
    product_id
    discount_status
    discount_type
    created_at
    updated_at
    deleted_at
    is_deleted
    discount_details {
      description
      discount_id
      discount_value
      is_deleted
      round_decimal
      updated_at
    }
    }
    product_action {
      dr
      favorites
      id
      sales
    }
    product_details {
      bonus_on_positive_review
      bonus_percentage
      brand_id
      card_mode
      details
      effectively_time
      effectively_type
      form_id
      id
      is_open_voucher
      is_open_form
      is_order_form
      limit_purchase
      logistics_type
      logistics_template {
        id
        billing_method
        dr
        is_active
        logistics_template_detail {
          id
          region
          template_id
          first_weight
          first_fee
          dr
          additional_weight
          additional_fee
        }
        mall_logistics_company {
          id
          name
        }
        name
      }
      max_redemption_percentage
      min_purchase_quantity
      product_code
      product_id
      shipping_price
      shipping_template_id
      sku_code
      sort_order
      stock_warning
      verification_number
      virtual_sales
      voucher_json
    }
      product_specification_middle_price{
      id
        spec_value
        selling_price
        market_price
      }
    product_images(take: 1, skip: 0) {
      id
      image_url
      image_type
      poster_html
    }
  }
  total: localhost_aggregateproduct(
    where: {product_categories: {is: {id: {equals: $product_categories}}}, name: {contains: $name}, is_deleted: {equals: $is_deleted}, product_dividend: {every: {is_deleted: {equals: 0}, is_custom_rule: {equals: $is_custom_rule}, dividend_type: {equals: $dividend_type}}}, store_id: {equals: $store_id}, product_tag_mapping: {every: {tag_id: {in: $tag_id}, dr: {equals: 0}}}, product_type: {equals: $product_type}, stock_status: {equals: $stock_status}, status: {equals: $status}}
  ) @transform(get: "_count.id") {
    _count {
      id
    }
  }
}
```
